    "summary": "The user expresses deep existential dread and nihilism triggered by contemplating the vastness of space, questioning the point of continuing to live. The assistant responds by validating the scientific accuracy of the user's perspective while reframing the meaning of life toward human connection and suggesting seeking support.",
